682	3985664	Freelance Web Designer - Front End Developer	New York, New York	<div class="p1"><b>Web Designer/Front End Developer</b></div>\n\n<div class="p2"> </div>\n\n<div class="p1">New York City-based strategic design and innovation firm is looking for an exceptionally talented person with 3–5 years experience to fill a freelance Web Designer/Front End Developer position. Because you live and breathe the web, and have excelled all your life in every aspect of hipster n3rdiness, you’ll be rewarded by working with some of the best design-thinkers in the business. You’ll collaborate with the experience design team to produce graphics and develop the front end code for websites and email communications. You’ll enjoy an fun, collaborative work environment in one of NYC’s best neighborhoods, creative freedom to do your best work, and a culture that fosters integration, growth, sharing and learning. </div>\n\n<div class="p2"> </div>\n\n<div class="p1"><b>Primary Responsibilities:</b></div>\n\n<ul class="ul1">\n\t<li class="li1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Help develop detailed graphics for projects once the visual direction has been established</li>\n\t<li class="li1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Take the lead in translating design comps into pixel-perfect HTML pages</li>\n\t<li class="li1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Collaborate with application developers to integrate back-end code</li>\n\t<li class="li1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Perform light scripting using PHP and JavaScript</li>\n\t<li class="li1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Work hands-on with popular content and marketing management platforms to install and skin</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class="p1"><strong>To qualify for this position, you need to have:</strong></div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A bachelor’s degree from an accredited university in a relevant field of study </li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Good graphic design skills and an understanding of usability for the web</li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Expert level skills with Photoshop, Illustrator, Dreamweaver (or similar), HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript </li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience translating design comps into final code that matches pixel for pixel </li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">The ability to generate standards-compliant, semantically rich code that separates content from design.</li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A thorough understanding of cross browser issues </li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong written and verbal communication skills are essential </li>\n\t<li class="p1" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">You must be extremely organized, dependable and have experience juggling multiple tasks/projects to be successful in this position </li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Filled	2016-05-26 19:30:28.71227	2016-06-01 00:00:08.127548	Motivate Design	Agency	t	Interaction Design
