nts:\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">6+ years design work with desktop or web interactive experiences.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Mastery of your tools (Sketch, Adobe Suite, etc.) The specific tool is not important but your mastery is!</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to prototype and show your ideas interactively (Motion studies, HTML5 prototypes, Invision or other prototype tools, etc) </li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A great portfolio showing your thought process and work</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Bachelors degree in Fine Arts, Graphic Design, visual communications, or a related field</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience working in a fast-paced Agile environment</li>\n</ul>\n <br />\n <br />\n 	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.338937	2016-08-11 20:00:08.767357	Wrap Media	In-house	t	UX Design, Product Design
