ices experience not required<br />\n●       Proficiency with Microsoft Word, Excel, and PowerPoint<br />\n●       Proficiency using online tools such as UserTesting.com, Optimal Workshop, UserZoom, ForeSee, Qualtrics, etc.<br />\n●       Ability to work cross functionally with analytics team to design data screens for recruiting<br />\n●       Strong project management, time management, and organizational skills<br />\n●       Strong written and verbal communication skills, including executive presentation skills<br />\n●       Professional yet engaging interaction style<br />\n 	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	On Hold	2016-05-26 19:30:28.659953	2016-06-01 00:00:08.183395	eTrade	\N	t	\N
