ed.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">HTML5 & CSS3, JSON / XML / HTML / Javascript / JQuery, Adobe Illustrator CS6 – a Plus.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Financial experience not a must: Any Information Architecture, Info Management, number/accounting exp a plus.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="text-align: center;"><em>** Please submit your portfolio with application**</em></div>\n <br />\n 	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	On Hold	2016-05-26 19:30:28.934117	2016-06-01 00:00:08.212375	Quovo, Inc.	\N	t	\N
