us.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Rapid prototyping</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Active (1)	2017-03-16 16:00:10.434244	2017-03-27 20:00:06.707246	McKinsey & Company	In-house	t	UX Design, Product Design
