ons, prototypes, and assisting in the testing of designs.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;"><strong>You will be successful in this role if you:</strong></span></span>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;">Like to move fast and are comfortable with failure. </span></span></li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;">You enjoy and know how to get stuff done in a rapidly changing environment. </span></span></li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;">You want to get in at the beginning, build from the ground up.</span></span></li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;">You want ownership over what you produce.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div><strong><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:georgia,serif;">Compensation / Perks:</span></span></strong></div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-