 multi-screen experiences</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Plan and estimate for highly complex projects</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Reinvent / streamline and apply brand identity systems, typography, photography, color and other ingredients to create innovative visual solutions that meet business and user needs</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Have a strong understanding of new technologies and production methodologies that supports the entire UX/Design process</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Must have a strong understanding of Drupal and other platform technologies.</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Create visual prototypes or screens</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Extremely detail oriented and provide quality assurance of all creative deliverables</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Contribute to the development of the creative team&#39;s culture and quality standards</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Continually elevate the creative level of the work</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Educate other team members, not exclusive to the creative team, through project development and performance management</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Collaborate with strategy, marketing and business development teams to activate new business opportunities.</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t <br />\n\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t <br />\n\t\t\t<strong>Qualifications</strong>\n\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">MA / BA</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">7+ years of publishing industry /agency experience</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong design portfolio with several large scale publishing websites</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to multi-task and work efficiently under pressure with careful attention to detail is a must</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A solid knowledge of the latest versions of applicable programs: Photoshop, Illustrator, PowerPoint, Keynote, etc.</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A detailed understanding of online production and optimization processes</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Passion for design and eagerness to mentor and elevate other creative professionals</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Self-motivated and organized</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience leading a team of designers, and production specialists</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Knowledge of foundation and bootstrap</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Excellent communication skills including ability to articulate creative concepts and rationale to other team members and client</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A solid understanding of information architecture and UX practices</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience working in a large global team environment</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience presenting to business and marketing teams</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t <br />\n\t\t\t<strong>Key competencies & skills:</strong>\n\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Photoshop Creative Suite</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Illustrator</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">InDesign</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Web optimization tools</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Knowledge of Adobe DPS (Nice to have)</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong understanding of frontend code, HTML, JavaScript etc. Front end development skills are a nice to have</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n <br />\n <br />\n 	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.69805	2016-06-01 00:00:08.428585	IBT Media	In-house