plain Complex Design Decisions</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Agile/Waterfall Environments</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Relevant Desktop/Mobile Technologies</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">High-level knowledge of UI design</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Familiar with the publishing industry and editorial content strategy</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><strong>Notes:</strong></div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Marketing, engineering and product work across all 4 business units. UX floats between business units as needed.​​</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Engineering team is in house</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Located in Hells Kitchen (upper 40s and 8th ave)</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Will start on 2 major projects for 4-6 months</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">They work collaboratively across departments and use JIRA</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">There is no visual/creative team - so UX/UI designers will be responsible for hi-fi design comps</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.225759	2016-08-11 20:00:10.403398	Media Bistro Holdings	In-house	t	UX Design, UI Design, Interaction Design
