ility sessions <br />\n<br />\n• Continued competitive awareness for product best-in-class. <br />\n<br />\nFront End Build QA <br />\n<br />\n• Leverage tools efficiently to communicate enhancement specification & capture defects (JIRA, Confluence, <br />\n<br />\netc.) <br />\n<br />\n• Work side-by-side with a Front End Web Development to build and validate all visual/functional <br />\n<br />\nenhancements <br />\n<br />\n• Ensure visual & interactive integrity of front-end build <br />\n<br />\n• Validate all UI states have been implemented to specifications & standards<br />\n<br />\nPresentation Support <br />\n<br />\n• Support preparing decks as needed for better communication of a concept <br />\n<br />\n• Partner with various creative leads to organize layouts and deliver for executive presentation <br />\n<br />\nQUALIFICATIONS <br />\n<br />\n• Sophisticated sense of visual design/style <br />\n<br />\n• Passionate advocate of for usability & user experience <br />\n<br />\n• UI visual design and interaction design expertise a plus <br />\n<br />\n• Ability to translate complex design challenges into clear, customer-friendly experiences<br />\n<br />\n• Working understanding of ecommerce and usability best practices<br />\n<br />\n• Collaborative, inclusive and flexible team member <br />\n<br />\n• Resourceful self-starter who gets things done <br />\n<br />\n• Highly organized with extreme attention to detail <br />\n<br />\n• Ability to manage multiple priorities and meet deadlines in a fast-paced environment <br />\n<br />\n• Positive, constructive approach <br />\n<br />\nEXPERIENCE REQUIRED <br />\n<br />\n• Bachelor’s Degree (Design / Interactive) or equivalent design experience <br />\n<br />\n• 3-5 years Web visual design experience <br />\n<br />\n• Mastery of appropriate tools & technology <br />\n<br />\n• Advanced Photoshop <br />\n<br />\n• Working knowledge of Illustrator <br />\n<br />\n• Understanding of the capabilities relating to the use of front-end Web technologies, including HTML, CSS, <br />\n<br />\nJavaScript a benefit <br />\n<br />\n• Proven talent in graphic and interactive design <br />\n<br />\n• Retail/fashion brand or agency experience desired; ecommerce experience ideal <br />\n<br />\n• Design for tablet & mobile UI	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.207226	2016-06-07 16:00:08.422386	Victoria's Secret / Limited Brands	\N	t	\N
