713	5692676	Talent Acquisition Manager, Recruitment Marketing	New York, New York	<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">About UX Hires:</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">UX Hires is a niche placement and consulting agency in FIDI that focuses very specifically on UI/UX practitioners  and  the companies that are looking to transform their business through improved consumer-focused design.  As the recruiting arm of a UX innovation agency, Motivate Design, we were unsatisfied with many staffing agencies&#39; recruiting processes and inattention to the nuances of the UX industry, so we decided to fulfill our clients staffing requests ourselves.</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Our roadmap:</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">We’re growing because companies are beginning to focus more on UX and we are recognized as leaders in our field.  Our team is looking for a Talent Acquisition Manager, Recruitment Marketing; a business-minded lead-off and clean-up hitter who leverages the branding, PR and marketing efforts of the company to effectively manage the sales and candidate pipeline. We are looking for a matchmaker to join our current dynamic duo and make it a trifecta powerhouse for sourcing and placing the best UX talent in the industry.  </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Your role:</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Your role will be to work with the team to identify and contract with existing, new and relevant clients, update our sourcing strategy to unclog our current placement bottleneck and expand the brand through active outreach.  To reiterate, we are redefining the antiquated recruiting approach by eliminating internal competition and by promoting a team-based strategy. We own a very niche segment of the market that focuses specifically on UX talent whom we nurture, groom, and ultimately place once a very thorough vetting process has occurred. Your job is to help optimize that process.</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Who are you?</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">You are looking for a challenge, you’re looking for a place to contribute strategically to the growth of an organization, and you’re looking for an opportunity to up your game. UX Hires and Motivate Design have established ourselves as the premium design and research firm in New York City. Your job will be to properly represent our brand in our interactions with candidates and new and existing clients.  You are hungry, organized, passionate and confident. Not only do you possess excellent written communication abilities, but you can look people in the eye when you’re speaking to them and have a knack for relationship building. We want you to use your interpersonal skills, your network and your passion for business development to help grow a quality business.</div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Primary Responsibilities of Role:</div>\n\n<ul style="list-style-position: outside; margin: 10px 0px; padding-left: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Assist in the broadening of the candidate pool using social media, interesting marketing tactics and general experience</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">With an understanding of our candidate pool and our reach, identify new and existing clients.</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Direct the funnel - don’t just cast a ‘wide net’, but help direct our marketing efforts to attract great candidates that best reflect our brand, our vision, and the industry.</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Break the bottleneck - Assist in a more optimal ‘matching’ of our candidates with clients’ needs</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Assist in the division of sourcing responsibilities between our current recruiters on staff</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Devise a supplemental value added component to any client relationship such that client expectations are exceeded by their engagement with us.</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Ensure that signed contracts are in place before any work is committed on our behalf</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Help optimize the company’s messaging and related collateral</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Manage and communicate the company’s overall pipeline of new business opportunities to the Executive Team</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Provide periodic (at least weekly) updates to the management team with pipeline metrics</div>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </div>\n\n<div style="margin: 1px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Qualifications:</div>\n\n<ul style="list-style-position: outside; margin: 10px 0px; padding-left: 25px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">BA/BS with 2-10 years of experience, preferably for technical and/or design related roles</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Corporate and/or staffing agency experience</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Exceptional communication skills - Must be comfortable speaking with clients and candidates alike</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">Attention to detail, excellent grammar and no typos - we represent a pixel-perfect design agency</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div style="margin: 1px 0px;">A desire to improve and innovate on the standard recruiting model</div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="list-style: disc outside; margin-left: 15px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A desire to work in a truly collaborative environment that values teamwork and recognizes working together creates greater success for everyone</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Filled	2016-05-26 19:30:28.938927	2016-08-29 16:00:17.25454	Internal Posting	\N	t	\N
