722	5605301	Interactive Art Director	San Francisco, CA	<div style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding-top: 0px; font-family: maven_proregular; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="color:#000000;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><u><strong>Overview:</strong></u><br />\nOur client is looking for an outstanding Interactive Art Director with strong interests and capabilities in the design of engaging website user experiences. The candidate must be a talented interactive designer whose work is clean, modern, inspiring, and empathetic. A designer who has the skill not only to create high-quality graphics for their website, but also the ability to apply the creatives in the context of a user-centered design approach. In-depth understanding of interactive visual design principles and desire to push conceptual thinking and the latest design and technology trends will be critical in creating experiences that connect with their customers.<br />\n<br />\nThe role is part of the Web Marketing & Strategy team, responsible for their public websites. The candidate will be the lead designer for the public website, responsible for website user experience and branding, and working closely with marketing and product creative teams to ensure common experience and brand representation across all interaction channels.<br />\n<br />\nThe ideal candidate will thrive in a work environment that requires strong problem solving skills and independent self-direction, coupled with an aptitude for team collaboration and open communication.<br />\n<br />\n<u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></span></span></span></div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding-top: 0px; font-family: maven_proregular; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,g