efficient while managing RFP responses. You’ll coordinate the response with the relevant parties and ensure it properly represents our company, our brand and our capabilities.</span></li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Manage and communicate the company’s overall pipeline of new business opportunities </span>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Effective use of CRM and project management tools with clear documentation of interaction touch points.</span></li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Be meticulous about where we are in the life of each opportunity</span></li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Be able to speak knowledgeably about the updated status of the pipeline</span></li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Join sales meetings and summarize the minutes for an effective follow up</span></li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Utilize effective listening skills to to synthesize and see the actual client problem and then articulate our response and solution in a way that resonates</span></li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;">Optimize the company’s decks and related sales collateral</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div><span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"> <br />\n<span style="font-size:14px;">Accountabilities:</span></span></div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="font-