737	4761790	Director of Interaction and Web Design	New York, New york	<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"><strong>Director, Web and Interaction Design</strong></u><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Work where art and technology meet!  Lead a team building compelling and intuitive experiences for a sophisticated, design-savvy user base. Our client, a leading aspirational e-commerce/marketplace site specializing in luxury and one-of-a-kind products is adding a Director of Interaction and Web Design to their Product team. </span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;"> </span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">With strong financial backing, our client is a unique blend of expert curators and seasoned Internet executives from companies including Ebay, Gilt, Google, FreshDirect, Mlb.com and Twitter.  They have become the go-to source for the world&#39;s leading interior designers and consumers to find antiques, vintage furniture, jewelry, vintage fashion and fine art.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">As the Director of our Interaction and Web Design team, you will be leading a talented group of interaction designers, web designers and user research interns. Candidates should possess a passion for great design, a strong aesthetic sensibility, and the ability to design simple solutions to complex problems. You should also be able to manage projects as well as people.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">As a member of the leadership team, you will partner with various members of our Product Management organization along with other departments to build the most compelling product experiences. Candidates must be creative problem solvers, innovative designers, and passionate user advocates. You must also thrive in a fast-paced, team-based, and results-focused environment.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Job Requirements</u><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Manage and mentor a team of talented interaction designers (including UI/visual) and user researchers.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Develop design processes that will help the team scale and produce well-considered designs.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Work with team to produce user experience strategy and develop next generation concepts.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Contribute significantly to strategic design initiatives, from defining our style guidelines, mobile design strategy to site architecture for consumer seller facing experiences.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Partner with a wide range of stakeholders from concept to creation, including product managers, marketing, user research, developers, and testing.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Comfortable in an agile environment of rapid iteration and experimentation, prototyping at various levels of fidelity.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Have command of various applications related to prototyping and user interface design (Indesign, Photoshop, Illustrator, Omnigraffle, etc).</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Possess strong verbal, written and visual presentation skills with a deep understanding of the value in storytelling.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Well versed in collaborative design techniques, rapid prototyping, UI design, UI patterns, time-based visual design and information architecture.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    Aware of current trends in design patterns, information visualization and current web technologies such as HTML 5, CSS3, Javascript, gestural UI, animation, etc.</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    At least 7+ years of experience designing consumer facing web applications</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">•    3+ years of managing/mentoring junior designers</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Education</u><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Advanced degree in Human Computer Interaction, Design, or other related discipline preferred</span><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;" />\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">Extras</u>\n<ul style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal;">\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><u>​</u>Unlimited paid time off</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Weekly white linen lunches</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Snacks</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Full benefits & 401k</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Paid family leave</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Commuter benefits</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">In-office yoga</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:29.102926	2016-06-01 00:00:09.487124	1stDibs	\N	t	\N
