.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Delivering status updates to key stakeholders</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Hosting clients at the office when running usability testing and other workshops</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n \n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">QUALIFICATIONS</span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The successful candidate will have some experience in project management and operations and meets the following prerequisites:</span></span></div>\n\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Must be enrolled in, or a recent graduate of, a four year college or university</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Strong organizational and time management skills</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Must be detail-oriented with a strong work ethic</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Exhibited ability to communicate effectively visually, verbally, and through writing</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Ability to work independently as well as be a contributing member to a team</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Commitment to see projects through from start to finish</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Ability to handle multiple tasks while meeting deadlines</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Excellent presentation skills</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-0d81-f1f9-dad00327f1d5"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Strong knowledge of and skills in Microsoft Office</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.820104	2017-02-24 21:00:07.526497	Motivate Design	In-house	t	\N
736	5137125	Senior UX Designer	New York, NY	<div style="text-align: center;"><strong>SENIOR UX/INTERACTION DESIGNER</strong></div>\n<br />\nWe are please to be assisting our client,a travel oriented startup (B2B & B2C products and services,) in their search for a strong Senior UX/Interaction Designer with research skills. They have very solid funding and a management team of veterans from the travel industry.<br />\n<br />\n<u>Overview</u> <br />\nRole will be to help define the &#39;what&#39; and &#39;how&#39; of their products and since it&#39;s a start-up, won&#39;t mind doing anything else they need. Will be working collaboratively to render the experience design for their products. In this capacity, you will be responsible for researching, designing, and prototyping new user experiences based on product requirements. You will ensure the design of their products support their requirements to a high level of quality.<br />\n<br />\n"Deliverables include research reports, sketches, models (of all sorts), prototyping, and documentation -whatever is required for proper implementation (and nothing more). You will be able to deliver in a fast-paced and changing environment, working along side management, marketing, product managers, developers and other designers. Collaboration is key to how we work, whether it&#39;s with a cross-functional team or within the design team. You will welcome input and be happy to support your colleagues to create the best products. Your projects will range from well-defined executions of business requirements to blue-sky explorations."<br />\n<br />\n<u>Need to haves</u>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">All candidates must have an on-line portfolio showcasing user experience work for desktop and touch devices.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">5 years work experience creating world-class user experience designs across device experiences.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Exceptional interaction design skills and a strong understanding of human or activity-centered design techniques</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Design Research:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Able to distill loads of information into actionable design principles</li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong problem finding and solving skills</li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Highly skilled in prototyping at the appropriate fidelity</li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong knowledge of technical capabilities and constraints across devices, and an interest to engage with emerging technologies</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Excellent collaboration and communication skills\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Enthusiasm for an iterative design process, driven by group critique.</li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to communicate design through sketches, models, and prototypes.</li>\n\t\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Outstanding written and verbal communication skills, including the ability to present work with conviction</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Passion for travel</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Bachelors Degree in Design, similar or equivalent experience</li>\n</ul>\n<u>Nice to Haves (Not Required)</u>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to prototype in HTML/CSS/JavaScript </li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Travel industry and e-commerce experience</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:29.097293	2016-06-01 00:00:09.558152	Stealth Travel	\N	t	\N
720	5669714	UX/UI Designer	New York, New York	The Client: <br />\nOur client&#39;s mission is to help connect entrepreneurs, investors, and advisors to create opportunity for every member of the entr<span style="font-size:12px;">epreneurial economy. With s</span>trong funding and rapidly growing revenue, they are making waves.<br />\n<br />\nThe Role:<br />\nThis role is junior to mid level. As a UX Designer for our client, you will be a driving force in creating a world-class user experience for their customers. By working closely with top notch Engineers, Product Managers, and UX Designers, as well as with colleagues in Customer Support during all stages of the product development cycle, you will lead efforts to collect and use customer insights to inspire and inform product design decisions. Your focus will be to create intuitive, professional, and aesthetically appealing features that empower customers to find the connections and information they need to succeed.<br />\n<br />\nOur client is looking for a critical thinker with an impeccable design sense and an affinity towards customer-centric product experiences. An ideal candidate will have strong attention to detail, a sound technical foundation, and experience building habit forming easy-to-use technology products.<br />\n<br />\nResponsibilities:\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Identify the needs of the user and understand the market opportunity, and use this information to create a first-class interface.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Collaborate with fellow designers, product managers, engineers, data analysts, and client facing teams to design, launch, and iterate on high-impact products</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Develop detailed wireframes, mockups, and prototypes to effectively communicate interaction and design ideas</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Provide thought leadership on usability of new and existing products, and advance initiatives for improving the end-to-end user experience</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Measures of Success</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Your success at our client will be measured by the performance of the products you work on in terms of driving user growth, engagement and retention, and liquidity.</li>\n</ul>\n<span style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Day to Day:</span><br />\n<span style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Start with morning standups - very involved with product teams, exchanging input across 2 primary product teams (back end search and mobile interface) - </span>Working with the 2 senior designers currently on the team, engineers, and product managers - will be doing research through prototyping.<br />\n<br />\nQualifications:\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">BA/BS degree in Computer Science, Interaction Design, Human Computer Interaction or related field</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Portfolio of experience designing web-based and mobile applications in a fast-paced, agile environment</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Demonstrated understanding of design principles, interaction design, and need to have some visual/typography abilities - (don&#39;t need to be too advanced with visual design)</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience and interest in designing and executing user tests and usability studies to direct product designs and priorities</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Excellent communication and teamwork skills</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Filled	2016-05-26 19:30:28.997358	2016-06-01 00:00:09.650769	Axial	\N	f	\N
731	5238157	Director of UX & Product Design	Santa Cruz, CA	<div style="text-align: center;">DIRECTOR, UX & PRODUCT DESIGN</div>\n<br />\nWe are honored to be representing our client, an emerging presence in business intelligence software, in their search for a Director of UX & Product Design. The success of their SaaS business intelligence platform products makes it easy for the 250+ industry leading clients to create custom data experiences that access the data in a context that is meaningful to their needs. to them in so everyone in the business can explore the data that matters to them, in the context that makes it truly meaningful. The company is headquartered in Santa Cruz, California, with offices in San Francisco, New York and London.<br />\n <br />\nThe director they hire will understand the power of good design - on user experience, brand recognition and environment. He/she will sweat the details, from pixel-crafting and clear copy to deep thought about the hard choices that need to be made to produce software that does what people want, bringing elegance and simplicity to complex areas.<br />\n <br />\nHe/she will  craft the vision, team and design philosophy for their products and will lead product design efforts from concept to production, shaping the entire user flow for working with data, designing dashboards and collaboration.<br />\n <br />\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Define the end-user front-end experience. Manage the consistent expression of look, feel, and voice in the product.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Brainstorm and create new design concepts and user experiences from abstract ideas.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Help establish a product vision and direction in conjunction with cross-functional stakeholders.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Produce assets (redlines, icons, images, color and type specs, etc.) and consult as needed to create and validate visual designs as they appear in our products.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Partner with PMs, engineers, and analysts to oversee the design of a product from conception until launch (and then some).</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Build a Design team to meet the growing needs of our SaaS product</li>\n</ul>\n <br />\nQUALIFICATIONS\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">Experience designing enterprise software products, and a portfolio of related work.</span> </li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience as a "player-coach" who is hands but can build a team over time.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Current knowledge of design trends and standards, tempered with the wisdom to know when to break the mold.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A passion for iterative design and AN understands of how first drafts are always imperfect, or even downright wrong.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Extremely high standards. You believe that software is an act of empathy and want to ship the best possible experience to customers.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Basic prototyping capabilities in HTML/CSS and potentially some Javascript. Coffeescript or Ruby, or Angular javascript library experience a PLUS.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience with Photoshop, Illustrator or Sketch.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Know how to craft clean, quick supporting copy.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Familiarity with / have used business intelligence tools like Splunk, Microstrategy, Business Objects, Cognos, Tableau, etc, or know how to write the occasional SQL query a PLUS</li>\n</ul>\n<br />\n <br />\nTHIS POSITION IS LOCATED IN SANTA CRUZ BUT CANDIDATES CAN BE FROM ANYWHERE IN THE BAY AREA AS LONG THEY CAN COMMIT TO 3 DAYS IN THE OFFICE (accommodations provided.) <br />\n<br />\nRelocation assistance also offered.<br />\n <br />\n 	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:29.064055	2016-06-01 00:00:09.563534	Looker	\N	t	\N
693	5267479	User Experience Design Manager	San Francisco, California	<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">User Experience Design </span></span></span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 21px; white-space: pre-wrap;">Manager</span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Our Client, </span></span><span style="line-height: 20.7999992370605px;">a successful 12 year-old SaaS based company located inside San Francisco,</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> is seeking a User Experience Design Manager to join their team and help bring world-class user experiences to their customers. Their products are changing the way business is handled in their niche sector. They have over 50 million users in countries around the world and are just getting started!</span></span></span></div>\n \n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">--About the Job--</span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You will be leading a team of 4-7 UX designers responsible for a wide swath of their product ecosystem. Our client wants you to help them grow as designers and create top-notch stuff. You’ll act as a &#39;wise sage, a therapist, a champion, a teacher, and a designer all in one day&#39;. As part of the larger User Experience team, you’ll help lead and develop the culture of design as they become a force to be reckoned with. </span></span></span></span></div>\n<br />\n<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 21px; white-space: pre-wrap;">--Team Structure--</span><br />\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">The team consists of 14 designers. They have a dedicated research team, and the designers have T-shaped skill sets and work very collaboratively.</span></span>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br />\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">--About You--</span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Our client is not just looking for a designer or a manager, they&#39;re looking for a user experience leader. To them, that means:</span></span></span></span></div>\n \n\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You’re an expert.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You have a deep passion for usability. You also know that being usable is only the beginning of the conversation.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You’re a people person. </span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You’re a good listener and know the value of letting someone rant. You build strong relationships and can motivate a whole team with one hand tied behind your back.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You foster collaboration.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You like to share the design process across the design team, and with other disciplines.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You see systems and believe in consistency.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> While a designer is solving a local problem, you’re seeing how it affects other parts of the ecosystem. </span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You have opinions about how process that doesn’t begin and end at the words “lean” or “agile”.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> Getting things done takes an understanding of design and development processes, and an understanding of people. </span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You can do, but you can also teach.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You know that people are our best asset and want to mentor and grow them. You’re interested in where they are now and what they want to accomplish.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You are great at giving good feedback.</span><span style="font-weight: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You’re an expert at how to help designers grow their solutions and grow themselves through constructive feedback.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You value results.</span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You know that design is nothing in a vacuum. Without measuring success, we’re just guessing. </span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You think strategically, execute locally.</span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> You know what you’re working on at any given moment is only a piece in the experience ecosystem and design to affect and integrate into that context.</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">You love what you do.</span><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;"> This isn’t just work, it’s one of your passions. </span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><br />\n<span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">--Benefits--</span></span></span></span></div>\n\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844-6d5c-43dc-5a4ae41a7735"><span style="vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Pre-IPO Stock</span></span></span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.5;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-7e2b7304-7844