jects will range from well-defined executions of business requirements to blue-sky explorations."</div>\n<br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;" />\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">Need to haves</u>\n\n<ul style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">All candidates must have an on-line portfolio showcasing user experience and visual design work for desktop and touch devices.</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">5 years work experience creating world-class user interface design across device experiences.</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Exceptional interaction design skills and a strong understanding of human or activity-centered design techniques</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Design Research, research, research!\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Able to distill loads of information into actionable design principles</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong problem finding and solving skills</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Highly skilled in prototyping at the appropriate fidelity</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong knowledge of technical capabilities and constraints across devices, and an interest to engage with emerging technologies</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Excellent collaboration and communication skills:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">You work well with others and do not subscribe to a &#39;heroic designer&#39; mentality.</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Enthusiasm for an iterative design process, driven by group critique.</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to communicate design through sketches, models, and prototypes.</li>\n\t\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Outstanding written and verbal communication skills, including the ability to present work with conviction</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Passion for <span class="il" style="background: rgb(255, 255, 204);">travel</span></li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Be self-motivated, work with minimal supervision, and support multiple projects concurrently.</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Able to function independently and in a cross-functional team environment.</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Bachelors Degree in Design, similar or equivalent experience</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Authorization to work in the US. No visa sponsorships.</li>\n</ul>\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">Nice to Haves</u>\n\n<ul style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal;">\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to prototype in HTML/CSS/JavaScript</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Mobile design experience familiarity with mobile development</li>\n\t<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;"><span class="il" style="background: rgb(255, 255, 204);">Travel</span> industry and e-commerce experience</li>\n</ul>\n<u style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, s