otypes</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Design to satisfy the needs and motivations of people</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Deliver a seemingly endless supply of solutions and ideas for the problems at hand</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Thrive in a highly collaborative, fast-paced, agile startup environment</li>\n</ul>\n <br />\n<u>Requirements:</u>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">At least 10 years experience in user experience design</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to lead and manage large design initiatives</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Expert ability to create flow charts, wireframes, prototypes and sitemaps</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A passion for user experience design, from user research thru released product</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to communicate your ideas to a wide variety of key stakeholders</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A belief that critique and collaboration can enhance any idea</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Mastery of standard design tools (e.g. Adobe Creative Suite, OmniGraffle)</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">A portfolio demonstrating superior user experience design skills</li>\n</ul>\n <br />\n<u>Bonus if you have:</u>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience designing for responsive websites</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience designing for mobile and tablet form factors</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience workin