isites</u>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Minimum of 7-10 years’ experience in Experience Design</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong web and mobile design experience required</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Knowledge of the agile software development process</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">You should inspire your peers and more junior team members to learn and expand their skill set, guiding them in the right direction.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">It is a plus is you have interest in data visualization and can create stunning visuals.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Graphic design skills, including use of a diverse set of software such as Adobe suite, OmniGraffle, Balsamiq, Axure, or other tools for graphic design, visual design.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Experience with conducting user research, usability testing, A/B testing</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Rapid prototyping </li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Closed	2016-05-26 19:30:28.957286	2016-08-26 16:00:11.223835	McKinsey & Company	In-house	t	\N
660	5910848	Video Editing Intern	New York, New York	<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">SUMMARY</span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Motivate Design is a leading research-driven design and innovation agency in NYC. We work with our partners to create exceptional brand experiences that humanize technology, improve people&#39;s lives and create new value for their businesses. We are looking for an intern to work with the director of operations to manage projects this fall, with the potential to extend the internship into the spring.</span></span></div>\n \n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">JOB DESCRIPTION</span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The successful video editing intern will primarily be creating exceptional and meaningful shorts for use on our website. Video shorts will be created to showcase Motivate Design’s work on multiple case studies as well as to share our in-office work in a creative yet professional manner. The intern will also assist the design and marketing teams on additional internal and external projects throughout the term.</span></span></div>\n \n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">QUALIFICATIONS</span></span></div>\n\n<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">The successful candidate will bring enthusiasm, passion, and a strong desire to learn to the office daily. He or she has demonstrated abilities primarily in video editing, but also ideally in visual/graphic design, and meets the following prerequisites:</span></span></div>\n\n<ul style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;">\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Must be enrolled in, or a recent graduate of, a four-year college or university</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Experience in and passion for videography and filmmaking</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Strong collaborative spirit with ability to communicate effectively visually, verbally, and through writing</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Passion for human-centered design and innovation inspired by clear, purposeful, and beautiful user experiences</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Strong conceptual and out-of-the-box thinking, with passion for disruption and inciting change</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Ability to receive constructive criticism and apply it to work</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: transparent;">Exhibited fluency with iMovie, Final Cut, Axure, InDesign, Photoshop and Illustrator a plus</span></span></div>\n\t</li>\n\t<li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type: disc; font-size: 13.3333333333333px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">\n\t<div dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.7999999999999998;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span id="docs-internal-guid-5289fc5b-283c-85f4-4bc2-5debbab1d156"><span style="font-size: 13.3333333333333px; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; backgrou