rbally, and through writing</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Passion for user-centered design and clear, beautiful user experiences</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong conceptual and out-of-the-box thinking, with passion for finding disruptive solutions</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Strong sense of typography, color-theory, and visual hierarchy.</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Natural eye for smart design solutions across disciplines (from web design to print design)</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Ability to work iteratively, receive constructive criticism and apply it to work</li>\n\t<li style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">Extremely comfortable working in Illustrator, Indesign and Powerpoint. Experience using Sketch or Axure is a plus.</li>\n</ul>	\N	\N	\N	\N	t	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	Active (1)	2016-05-26 19:30:28.757548	2017-02-06 17:00:12.707023	Motivate Design	In-house	t	\N
